      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Start in the GitHub Copilot app for context.\n- Call out the main areas: Home, My Work, Automations, and Chat.\n- Frame this as the first invoice-review proof of concept.\n- Make clear this is still a local setup, not the final enterprise model.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the GitHub Copilot app. Briefly orient the viewer to the environment and the top-level navigation.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111553_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.15.31@2x.png"
