        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~25s",
      "narrative": "- Once inside the project, the POC gets more concrete.\n- Show how the work is organized across chat, actions, and canvas.\n- Chat steers the task.\n- Actions runs steps.\n- Canvas is where the agent starts to take shape.",
      "demo_actions": "Click through the project work areas and briefly point out chat, rubber duck, actions, agent merge, and canvas.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_111801_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.17.40@2x.png"
