        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- In this first version, the agent runs locally with MXC enabled.\n- That matters because the team can test the task while keeping documents inside a controlled sandbox.\n- It is a safe way to prove the review flow before expanding it.",
      "demo_actions": "Point to the local model setup and the MXC sandbox indicator. Explain why that matters in the POC stage.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_112324_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.20.38@2x.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": false,
      "locks": {
