        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~40s",
      "narrative": "- When we run it, the agent follows the same reasoning used later in the full demo.\n- It checks local contracts, receipts, batch records, quality status, milestone approvals, and invoice lines.\n- Then it returns a recommendation with supporting evidence.\n- This is the first proof that the task is workable.",
      "demo_actions": "Run the agent on a sample invoice. Show inputs, evidence access, and the resulting recommendation with cited support.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260617_112332_CleanShot 2026-06-17 at 11.20.07@2x.png"
    },
    {
