        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- So the local POC answers the first question.\n- Yes, the agent can do the job.\n- But it still needs real enterprise data, guardrails, hosted deployment, and broader access for the business.\n- That is the next step.",
      "demo_actions": "Pause on the result and summarize what worked in the local run and what is still missing for enterprise use.",
